            <a href="/#access" class="block py-3 pl-8 pr-4 text-primary font-bold hover:bg-light border-b border-border transition">アクセス</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="block py-4 px-4 bg-light text-center text-accent font-bold transition">お問い合わせ</a>
